requirements.full_sentence:
NBFCs shall communicate, not later than one month from the occurrence of any
change in:
(1) the names and residential addresses of the directors of the company;

The issues shall be governed by the following instructions:
(1) The minimum subscription per investor shall be ₹20,000 (Rupees Twenty
thousand);

(2) The issuance of private placement of NCDs shall be in two separate categories,
those with a maximum subscription of less than ₹1 crore and those with a minimum
subscription of ₹1 crore and above per investor;

(3) There shall be a limit of 200 subscribers for every financial year, for issuance of
NCDs with a maximum subscription of less than ₹1 crore, and such subscription
shall be fully secured;
